changelog:
goLive v1.4.6 update includes:
- Much much 
faster syncing speed (this is achieved by changing the database 
online so, if you want to transfer the saved titles you have 
online you must sync the items to local bookmark first, it's a 
bit technical but it is what it is)
- Soundtrack section is 
back working
- UI fix
- Bug fix and general quality of life 
update
Minimum Android version required to run the app: 5.0 or 
Lollipop or up
